            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Hec sunt privilegia, honores, iurisdictiones et consuetudines curie communis
                        et hominum de Guastalla. In primis, commune et homines de Guastalla in curia
                        et penes potestatem et curiam Guastalle debent habere quatuor iuratores de
                        hominibus Guastalle qui pares curie apellantur, qui debent facere
                        condemnaciones et absolutiones maleficiorum et ofensionum que fierent et
                        perpetraverint in districtu et curia Guastalle, tam de eis in quibus
                        vindictam sanguinis exercerint quam de alliis maleficiis et offensionibus in
                        robis et personis. Item quod <geogName ref="#estates/40"
                            key="#Curtes #Army #Districtio">curia <placeName ref="#places/33"
                                key="#Curtes #Army #Districtio">Guastalle</placeName></geogName> est
                            <rs key="#Curtes #Districtio">curia regalis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Districtio">iurisdictio</rs> per se habet in omnia <rs
                            key="#Districtio">imperium</rs> et plenam iurisdictionem, habendo <rs
                            key="#Army #Districtio">gladii potestatem</rs>. Item quod <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/128" key="#Local_institutions #City_authorities"
                                ><rs key="#Local_institutions #City_authorities">commune</rs> et
                            homines de Guastalla</orgName> toto tempore quo fuerint in <rs
                            key="#Army">servicio</rs> iverint et steterint suis propris expensis et
                        suis risigis et periculis in rebus et personis, sine aliquo gravamine et
                        expensis <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/99">communis <placeName
                                ref="#places/58">Cremone</placeName></orgName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
